{
  "page": "Drogo's khalasar",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> This article or section is a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stub\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help \"A Wiki Of Ice And Fire\" by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Drogo%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a> and/or improving existing text.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Drogo's <i>khalasar</i></b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> horde composed of forty thousand men. The <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> is led by <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">Khal</a></i> <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Members\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Members</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Drogo%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Drogo%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After the wedding of Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>, the <i>khalasar</i> leaves <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a> for <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Dothrak\" title=\"Vaes Dothrak\">Vaes Dothrak</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Drogo's <i>khalasar</i> breaks up into separate new <i>khalasars</i> after the death of Khal Drogo.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Members\">Members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Drogo%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Members\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><i>Khal</i> <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Khaleesi\" title=\"Khaleesi\">Khaleesi</a></i> <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>, Drogo's wife, who forms her own <i><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daenerys_Targaryen%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen&#39;s khalasar (page does not exist)\">khalasar</a></i> after his death</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Ko\" title=\"Ko\">Ko</a></i> <a href=\"/index.php/Cohollo\" title=\"Cohollo\">Cohollo</a>, Drogo's <a href=\"/index.php/Bloodrider\" title=\"Bloodrider\">bloodrider</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Qotho\" title=\"Qotho\">Qotho</a>, Drogo's bloodrider</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Haggo\" title=\"Haggo\">Haggo</a>, Drogo's bloodrider</li>\n<li><i>Ko</i> <a href=\"/index.php/Pono\" title=\"Pono\">Pono</a>, who went on to form his own <i><a href=\"/index.php/Pono%27s_khalasar\" title=\"Pono&#39;s khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> after Drogo's death</li>\n<li><i>Ko</i> <a href=\"/index.php/Jhaqo\" title=\"Jhaqo\">Jhaqo</a>, who went on to form his own <i><a href=\"/index.php/Jhaqo%27s_khalasar\" title=\"Jhaqo&#39;s khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> after Drogo's death</li>\n<li><i>Ko</i> <a href=\"/index.php/Aggo\" title=\"Aggo\">Aggo</a>, of Daenerys's <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khas\" title=\"Khas\">khas</a></i></li>\n<li><i>Ko</i> <a href=\"/index.php/Jhogo\" title=\"Jhogo\">Jhogo</a>, of Daenerys's <i>khas</i></li>\n<li><i>Ko</i> <a href=\"/index.php/Rakharo\" title=\"Rakharo\">Rakharo</a>, of Daenerys's <i>khas</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Quaro\" title=\"Quaro\">Quaro</a>, of Daenerys's <i>khas</i>. Killed by Qotho.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mago\" title=\"Mago\">Mago</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rommo\" title=\"Rommo\">Rommo</a>, an aged <i><a href=\"/index.php/Jaqqa_rhan\" title=\"Jaqqa rhan\">jaqqa rhan</a></i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Irri\" title=\"Irri\">Irri</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Slave\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slave\">slave</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Handmaiden\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Handmaiden\">handmaiden</a> to Daenerys</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jhiqui\" title=\"Jhiqui\">Jhiqui</a>, a slave and handmaiden to Daenerys</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Doreah\" title=\"Doreah\">Doreah</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lysene</a> slave and handmaiden to Daenerys</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eroeh\" title=\"Eroeh\">Eroeh</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Lhazar\" title=\"Lhazar\">Lhazareen</a> slave and handmaiden to Daenerys. Raped and killed by Jhaqo, Mago and six others.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Drogo%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_3\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 3\">Chapter 3</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-